'''''Star Wars Insider'' 89''' is the 89th issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'', released in [[August]] [[2006]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]"
*"[[Skywalking]]"
*"[[Jedi Library (department)|Jedi Library]]" &mdash; [[Darth Bane: Path of Destruction|Darth Reign]] {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Drawn by the Force]]" &mdash; [[Star Wars: Dark Empire II Second Edition|The Emperor's Final Fate]] {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace|Dan Wallace]]}}
*"[[Jabba's Collection]]" &mdash; Han Shoots Fir&ndash; Ah, You Know
*"[[Set Piece|Technical Readout]]" &mdash; Escape From Cloud City {{C|by [[Chris Trevas|Christopher Trevas]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|Ask the Master]]" &mdash; Maybe Luke Was a Bad Pilot, After All {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; The One That Almost Got Away! {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Best of Hyperspace]]" &mdash; What's the Story? {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and [[Bonnie Burton]]}}
*"[[Padawan's Corner|Padawan Corner]]" &mdash; How To Draw a Tusken Raider {{C|by [[Justin Lambros]]}}
*[[Bantha Tracks (department)|''Bantha Tracks'']] Vol. 20 {{C|edited by [[Mary Franklin]]}}

===Features===
*"[[ILM's Sizzling Mustafarian Summer]]" {{C|by [[Ron Magid]]}}
*:<small>'''Insider''' takes a look at some of this summer's biggest movies and how their senses-sizzling looks evolved from visual effects developed for the ''[[Star Wars]]'' prequels.</small>
*"[[Where Did You Dig Up That Old Fossil?]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>While the original theatrical versions of the ''Star Wars'' trilogy may not have been [[George Lucas]]' true vision of the films, they nevertheless are timeless testaments to the work of a hungry young filmmaker and his special effects artists, as well as enduring parts of our pop culture.</small>
*"[[Underworld: A Galaxy of Scum and Villainy]]" {{C|by [[Abel G. Peña]] and [[Ryan Kaufman (real person)|Ryan Kaufman]], illustrated by [[Joe Corroney]]}}
*:<small>For your eyes only! The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] presents a thorough rundown of the worst non-[[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] scum [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] has to offer from [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lords]] and [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] to [[Spice/Legends|spice]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] and [[Glitterstim/Legends|glitterstim]] peddlers.</small>
*"[[The Art of War (Star Wars Insider 89)|The Art of War]]" {{C|by [[Frank Parisi]]}}
*:<small>In the last of a three-part series examining [[Star Wars: Legacy|''Star Wars'' Legacy]], we talk to the series' visionary illustrator [[Jan Duursema]].</small>
*"[[Bricks, Whips, and Spaceships]]" {{C|by [[Ryan Jones]]}}
*:<small>From [[LEGO Star Wars II: The Original Trilogy]] to the mysterious [[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed|next-gen ''Star Wars'' video game]], the further adventures in a galaxy far, far away continue. Check out some of the upcoming games from the worlds of ''Star Wars'' and [[Indiana Jones]].</small>

